EXTRACT.P:
Small grains.
 Wheat, including only common wheat (
Triticum aestivum
), club wheat (
T. compactum
), durum wheat (
T. durum
) and Khorasan (
T. turanicum
); barley (
Hordeum vulgare
), including hull-less barley and excluding black barley; oats (
Avena sativa,
 and 
A. byzantina
), and hull-less oats (
A. Nuda
); rye (
Secale cereale
); flax (
Linum usitatissimum
); and buckwheat (
Fagopyrum esculentum
).
